      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Mechanical highlights include a documented VANOS system service and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014essential for long-term chassis rigidity. The powertrain delivers linear torque through individual throttle bodies, while the suspension has been maintained with OEM-spec bushings and upgraded dampers for precise turn-in. Showing honest cosmetic patina, this vehicle remains mechanically robust, providing the visceral, analog feedback expected of the M-division's hallmark engineering.",
