    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric induction. The S54B32 power unit features a high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, ensuring razor-sharp throttle response and a linear power delivery to the 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement, addressing the platform's primary structural concern. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution during corner exit. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver's car, the suspension maintains its original kinematics with upgraded polyurethane bushings for enhanced lateral stability and steering precision. A perfect candidate for the enthusiast seeking peak BMW M-division engineering in a usable, honest condition.",
